第 132 章)發出的食物業牌照的持有人<br />\n<br />\n📌個人和團體應該分別填寫邊張表格？<br />\n<strong>個人登記</strong><br />\nREO-41 中文 <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=ecf5b7c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\nREO-41 English <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28E&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=79c7592a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(E</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong>團體登記</strong><br />\nREO-42 中文 <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-42(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-42%28C&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=69c7a536\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-42(C</a>).pdf<br />\nREO-42 English <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-42(E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-42%28E&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=fcf54bde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-42(E</a>).pdf<br />\n自動填表機<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote/app.html?type=new-functional\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote%2Fapp.html%3Ftype%3Dnew-functional&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=c2328b79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote/app.html?type=new-functional</a><br />\n📌為何有REO-43表格?<br />\nREO-41與REO-43表格相通。<strong>如已登記普通選民 (地方 + 超區)，可使用REO43，改為功能界別選民（地方 + 飲食)</strong>。"}]}